<COREF ID="25049" TYPE="IDENT">The State Council</COREF> formally submitted <COREF ID="25050" TYPE="IDENT">a proposal *PRO* to establish <COREF ID="chtb_144-E7" TYPE="IDENT">the Chongqing directly governed municipality</COREF></COREF> to the 5th session of the Eighth National People 's Congress .
<COREF ID="25052" TYPE="IDENT">Chongqing</COREF> is one of the largest cities in <COREF ID="25062" TYPE="IDENT">China</COREF> with a long history of more than 3,000 years .
In <COREF ID="25062" TYPE="IDENT">China 's</COREF> southwestern region and the upper reaches of <COREF ID="25071" TYPE="IDENT">the Yangtze River</COREF> , <COREF ID="25052" TYPE="IDENT">it</COREF> is the largest municipal economic center and an important communications hub .
